episodes.title: Treehouse of Horror VII
episodes.plot: Bart's Siamese twin swells in the attic; Lisa's science experiment creates a miniature universe of advanced civilization; aliens possess Clinton and Dole.

episodes.title: You Only Move Twice
episodes.plot: After moving to another town for a new job, Homer must decide whether or not to stay when the family have a hard time with the transfer.

episodes.title: The Homer They Fall
episodes.plot: Homer becomes a boxer after Moe discovers his amazing ability to take a punch.

episodes.title: Burns, Baby Burns
episodes.plot: The Simpsons try to reunite Mr. Burns with Larry, his slovenly long-lost son.

episodes.title: Bart After Dark
episodes.plot: Marge leads a crusade against a local burlesque house after she discovers Bart working there.

episodes.title: A Milhouse Divided
episodes.plot: Homer questions the state of his marriage after Luann Van Houten demands a divorce from Kirk.

episodes.title: Lisa's Date with Density
episodes.plot: Lisa develops a crush on Nelson, and tries to reform him; Homer gets an autodialer and decides to make easy money with a telemarketing scam.

episodes.title: Hurricane Neddy
episodes.plot: After a hurricane destroys Ned Flanders' house, he suffers a nervous breakdown and is forced to confront repressed problems from his childhood.

episodes.title: El Viaje Misterioso de Nuestro Jomer
episodes.plot: After eating insanity peppers at a chili cook-off, Homer has a hallucination of a talking coyote urging him to find his soulmate.

episodes.title: The Springfield Files
episodes.plot: Special Agents Mulder and Scully arrive in Springfield after Homer claims to have seen an alien.

episodes.title: The Twisted World of Marge Simpson
episodes.plot: Marge enters the pretzel vending business, but when she fails, Homer recruits some help from the mob.

episodes.title: Mountain of Madness
episodes.plot: Homer and Mr. Burns get trapped in a snowed-in cabin during a company retreat.

episodes.title: Simpsoncalifragilisticexpiala(Annoyed Grunt)cious
episodes.plot: Marge is stressed from motherhood and hires a British nanny to help out around the house, who struggles to teach Bart and Lisa how to behave.

episodes.title: The Itchy & Scratchy & Poochie Show
episodes.plot: Homer is cast as Poochie, a new "Itchy and Scratchy" character designed to reverse declining ratings; a hip college student moves in with the Simpsons.

episodes.title: Homer's Phobia
episodes.plot: After Marge befriends John, a gay store owner, Homer worries that his presence will have a negative effect on Bart's sexuality.

episodes.title: Brother from Another Series
episodes.plot: Bart suspects a paroled Sideshow Bob is up to his old tricks when he is hired by his brother Cecil to assist in the construction of a dam.

episodes.title: My Sister, My Sitter
episodes.plot: Bart is outraged when Lisa becomes his babysitter.

episodes.title: Homer vs. the 18th Amendment
episodes.plot: After alcohol is banned in Springfield, Homer adopts the moniker of the "Beer Baron" to bootleg liquor, prompting an investigation from an uptight Treasury agent.

episodes.title: Grade School Confidential
episodes.plot: Bart discovers Principal Skinner and Mrs Krabappel kissing, and it's not long before the whole town knows of their secret affair.

episodes.title: The Canine Mutiny
episodes.plot: When the items Bart purchased with a fake credit card are repossessed, he claims that Santa's Little Helper is the dog he bought instead of his new pet, Laddie.

episodes.title: The Old Man and the Lisa
episodes.plot: Burns loses his fortune and recruits Lisa to help him get it back.

episodes.title: In Marge We Trust
episodes.plot: Marge becomes a church counselor; Homer discovers his face on a Japanese detergent logo.

episodes.title: Homer's Enemy
episodes.plot: Homer's laziness begets the ire of his industrious but arrogant new co-worker Frank Grimes; Bart buys a run-down factory for a dollar.

episodes.title: The Simpsons Spin-Off Showcase
episodes.plot: Troy McClure presents three spinoffs: "Chief Wiggins, P.I.," "The Love-Matic Grandpa," and "The Simpson Family Smile-Time Variety Hour."

episodes.title: The Secret War of Lisa Simpson
episodes.plot: Bart is sent to a military school to be disciplined; Lisa, seeking a challenge, enrolls with him, but faces discrimination as the school's only girl cadet.
